Guidelines for writing an analysis in expert mode

 1. Entering the directory 'dumb/Build'

 2. Setting the environment variables by loading setup.sh or setup.csh according to your SHELL

 3. Entering the directory '~/madanalysis5/dumb/Build/SampleAnalyzer/User/Analyzer'

 4. Editing Analysis 'user.h' and 'user.cpp' files

 5. Entering the directory '/afs/cern.ch/work/a/acarvalh/phenoHH/madanalysis5/dumb/Build'

 6. Compiling with the command 'make'

 7. Writing a list of datasets

 8. Launching SampleAnalyzer with the list of datasets

